## DESCRIPTION

The slot logic implementaion is designed to reflect the real life slot logic for airports.
Therefore we have to imagine and adapte this system to the game. This feature will be available for airports with a slot logic. This feature will be enabled or disaabled by the user in the settings menu to avoid conflicting with ATC Online or other features.

## GAMEPLAY

### 1. When a leg is created, the slot time is set to the current time. For example if the flight is scheduled to depart at 12:00, the slot time will be set to 12:00. If I pass the slot time, I will get a penalty and another slot time will be assigned to me. 
